OL,3,CCritically injured man arrested for
OL,4,Cmurder over woman's death
OL,6,FA murder investigation has been
OL,7,Flaunched after the death of a woman in
OL,8,FLeeds.
OL,10,FEmergency services were called to
OL,11,FFoster Square in the Belle Isle area
OL,12,Fof the city at 10.25am on Thursday 12
OL,13,FJune.
OL,15,FA 51-year-old woman was pronounced
OL,16,Fdead at the scene. Her family is being
OL,17,Fsupported by specially trained
OL,18,Fofficers.
